body:
Not that I don&#039;t believe that reports for a single don&#039;t stack, or that it only takes a single report to get someone punished, but a lot of new players might not know that report calling can contribute to a punishment and get confused as the official pages don&#039;t state this anywhere.

I might just be crazy though, and we might not need such a page (or it might already exist), but it would be nice.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
